  "subject": "Add demo for Control Loop Coordination.",
  "commit_message": "Add demo for Control Loop Coordination.\n\nJunit demo and config files added to template.demo.\n\nNew PIPEngine and Junit test added to guard.\nAlso bug in existing Junit test fixed.\n\nCode added to enable selection of embedded XACML PDPEngine\ninstead of current restful version.\n\nEnhancement to notification messages sent by drools archetype\nand updates to ensure correct operation of existing demo Junits.\n\nChange-Id: I2b1aa68bf4a147f532c1412b14a00cf1c15b9cc0\nIssue-ID: POLICY-1109\nSigned-off-by: Joshua Reich <jreich@research.att.com>\n",
